HEADWORD: Bismuthic
<hw>Bis"muth*ic</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Of or pertaining to bismuth; containing bismuth, when this element
has its higher valence; <as>as, <ex>bismuthic</ex> oxide</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bismuthiferous</ent>⟦br⟧
